{"id":868,"date":"2018-09-06T04:26:17","date_gmt":"2018-09-06T04:26:17","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/jorgezhang.com\/?p=868"},"modified":"2018-09-06T04:26:17","modified_gmt":"2018-09-06T04:26:17","slug":"more-influence-card-changes","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/jorgezhang.com\/2018\/09\/more-influence-card-changes\/","title":{"rendered":"More Influence Card Changes"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Hey everyone! I&#8217;m in the final phases of tweaking in terms of the influence cards. They have overall been pretty balanced, and people have enjoyed them a lot. However, there were a couple of cards that were consistently passed over, indicating that they were not very desirable, or too confusing. One major change is the elimination of all influence cards that require action points to use. While they were pretty interesting cards, it became clear that they were a bit too clunky. Even if they ultimately paid off, people didn&#8217;t like them because they ate into their actions.<\/p>\n<p><img data-attachment-id=\"713\" data-permalink=\"https:\/\/jorgezhang.com\/2018\/08\/influence-cards-pt-3\/lie-on-the-resume\/#main\" data-orig-file=\"https:\/\/i2.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/08\/Lie-on-the-Resume.png?fit=1000%2C1400&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1000,1400\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Lie on the Resume\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https:\/\/i2.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/08\/Lie-on-the-Resume.png?fit=214%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https:\/\/i2.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/08\/Lie-on-the-Resume.png?fit=731%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-713 alignnone\" src=\"https:\/\/i2.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/08\/Lie-on-the-Resume.png?resize=253%2C354&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"253\" height=\"354\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i2.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/08\/Lie-on-the-Resume.png?w=1000&amp;ssl=1 1000w, https:\/\/i2.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/08\/Lie-on-the-Resume.png?resize=214%2C300&amp;ssl=1 214w, https:\/\/i2.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/08\/Lie-on-the-Resume.png?resize=768%2C1075&amp;ssl=1 768w, https:\/\/i2.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/08\/Lie-on-the-Resume.png?resize=731%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 731w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 253px) 100vw, 253px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" \/><img data-attachment-id=\"876\" data-permalink=\"https:\/\/jorgezhang.com\/2018\/09\/more-influence-card-changes\/lie-on-the-resume-2\/#main\" data-orig-file=\"https:\/\/i1.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/Lie-on-the-Resume.png?fit=1000%2C1400&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1000,1400\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Lie on the Resume\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https:\/\/i1.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/Lie-on-the-Resume.png?fit=214%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https:\/\/i1.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/Lie-on-the-Resume.png?fit=731%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone  wp-image-876\" src=\"https:\/\/i1.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/Lie-on-the-Resume.png?resize=253%2C354&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"253\" height=\"354\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i1.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/Lie-on-the-Resume.png?w=1000&amp;ssl=1 1000w, https:\/\/i1.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/Lie-on-the-Resume.png?resize=214%2C300&amp;ssl=1 214w, https:\/\/i1.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/Lie-on-the-Resume.png?resize=768%2C1075&amp;ssl=1 768w, https:\/\/i1.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/Lie-on-the-Resume.png?resize=731%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 731w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 253px) 100vw, 253px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" \/><\/p>\n<p>This change was long-due ever since the change to Integrity. It also offers a more interesting decision: you can gain a burst of RP, but in exchange must maintain a high Integrity. After play-testing with it at 3 Integrity, I felt that it could be lowered to 2 Integrity as it was rarely worth it otherwise.<\/p>\n<p><img data-attachment-id=\"714\" data-permalink=\"https:\/\/jorgezhang.com\/2018\/08\/influence-cards-pt-3\/caffaine-pills\/#main\" data-orig-file=\"https:\/\/i2.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/08\/Caffaine-pills.png?fit=1000%2C1400&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1000,1400\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Caffaine pills\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https:\/\/i2.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/08\/Caffaine-pills.png?fit=214%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"ht