image-title=\"Well Behaved\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/Well-Behaved.png?fit=214%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/Well-Behaved.png?fit=731%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone  wp-image-878\" style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen-Sans, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;\" src=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/Well-Behaved.png?resize=274%2C384&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"274\" height=\"384\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/Well-Behaved.png?w=1000&amp;ssl=1 1000w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/Well-Behaved.png?resize=214%2C300&amp;ssl=1 214w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/Well-Behaved.png?resize=768%2C1075&amp;ssl=1 768w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/Well-Behaved.png?resize=731%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 731w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 274px) 100vw, 274px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Well Behaved is another special action that was modified. It&#8217;s gotten a significant buff now, but I feel that it is fair since it comes with a significant Happiness cost that comes with it&#8217;s own repercussions.<\/p>\n<p><img data-attachment-id=\"691\" data-permalink=\"https:\/\/jorgezhang.com\/2018\/08\/influence-cards-pt-1\/get-tutored\/#main\" data-orig-file=\"https:\/\/i1.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/08\/Get-Tutored.png?fit=1000%2C1400&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1000,1400\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;