ter\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https:\/\/i1.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/All-Nighter.png?fit=214%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https:\/\/i1.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/All-Nighter.png?fit=731%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone  wp-image-872\" style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen-Sans, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;\" src=\"https:\/\/i1.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/All-Nighter.png?resize=261%2C366&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"261\" height=\"366\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i1.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/All-Nighter.png?w=1000&amp;ssl=1 1000w, https:\/\/i1.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/All-Nighter.png?resize=214%2C300&amp;ssl=1 214w, https:\/\/i1.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/All-Nighter.png?resize=768%2C1075&amp;ssl=1 768w, https:\/\/i1.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/All-Nighter.png?resize=731%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 731w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 261px) 100vw, 261px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Get tutored was scrapped entirely, which was a bit sad since it has been here since the beginning. However, there already is the &#8220;private tutor&#8221; influence card, and since I want 8 of each color influence card I decided to make a new influence card. Pulling an All-Nighter was a theme that was never really explored before, and I think this card makes perfect thematic sense. One thing that this card helps solve is a lack of actions. It&#8217;s entirely possible to have a situation where you have too many Stats and not enough actions to Test Correct everything. That&#8217;s just one example: the flexibility this card provides is fantastic. I&#8217;m honestly not sure if this card is too expensive, or too cheap. Will have to test it to find out.<\/p>\n<p><img data-attachment-id=\"696\" data-p